</div>
</div>
<div class="col-4">
<div class="author-content">
<p><strong><a href="http://kk.org/cooltools/files/2008/06/13918651_603790483113973_1799207977_o.jpg"><img class="alignnone wp-image-27340" src="https://kk.org/cooltools/files/2008/06/13918651_603790483113973_1799207977_o-300x300.jpg" alt="13918651_603790483113973_1799207977_o" width="217" height="217" /></a>Mark Frauenfelder</strong> edits Cool Tools and develops editorial projects for Cool Tools Lab, LLC. If you’d like to submit a review, email him at editor {at} cool-tools.org (or use the Submit a Tool form).</p>
</div>
</div>
