<p><strong><a href="http://kk.org/cooltools/files/2008/06/13898183_602421513250870_1391167760_o.jpg"><img class="alignnone wp-image-27339" src="https://kk.org/cooltools/files/2008/06/13898183_602421513250870_1391167760_o-300x300.jpg" alt="13898183_602421513250870_1391167760_o" width="217" height="217" /></a>Claudia Dawson</strong> runs the Cool Tool website, posting items daily, maintaining software, measuring analytics, managing ads, and in general keeping the site alive. If you have a concern about the operation or status of this site contact her email is claudia {at} cool-tools.org.</p>
